  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1127496/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/d5e43008a033f89beed1e4aac60f2238.jpg\" style=\"height: 265px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t古今中外没有一个不骂人的人。说到用英语骂人，很多人第一反应的词就是&ldquo;F**k&rdquo;或者是&rdquo;B**ch&rdquo;。但是！！英语君告诉大家，其实骂人的词是有很多，也有不同程度的区分。如果在骂人的时候选错词，结果可能是用力过猛，真的伤人自尊，又或者是不痛不痒，你爱骂不骂。因此在这么博大精深的骂人艺术中，我们是有必要好好了解，既能骂得优雅，又能骂得精辟。下面英语君带大家看看，国骂中的三个不同程度级别的骂法。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/d3687709fff41ba1fab4708e3ec96919.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 25.1999988555908px; height: 538px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t首先，我们先来说说什么是国骂？<br />\n\t国骂：一个国家的通用侮辱别人人格的话。（简单来说就是骂人的话咯）<br />\n\t当然每个国家历史文化不一样，骂人的话也不尽相同。不过嘛，骂人的内容还是那几个：<br />\n\tThese included general swear words, words linked to race and ethnicity, gender and sexuality, body parts and health conditions, religious insults, as well as certain hand gestures.这一般骂人的话都和种族、民族、性别、性行为、身体的某个部分、身体状况、宗教辱骂或者是某些手势。<br />\n\t于是，我们把这些骂人的词分成四个级别：mild温和, medium中等, strong强 or strongest最强.</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/cdfc533444bf53569cfede349a14a0cd.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 348px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">一、Mild就想温柔地骂骂你</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">1.Arse屁股；饭桶</span><br />\n\te.g.&quot;Don't ask John for any advice over your financial affairs&rdquo; he doesn't know his arse from his elbow.&quot; &ldquo;别拿你的财务问题去请教约翰他屁都不懂。&rdquo;<br />\n\te.g. John, shift your arse and get the job finished. He's not ill; he's just work-shy! 约翰，别偷懒，把活儿干完。他没病，他只是想偷懒！<br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">2. Bugge卑鄙的人；麻烦事；滚开；同性恋者</span><br />\n\te.g. Bugger it! I've missed my plane!真倒霉，我没赶上飞机!<br />\n\te.g. She told me to bugger off.她叫我走开。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/2f3b775faaa75c6b73379bf3cc6832d6.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 400px; width: 400px;\" /><br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">3. Crap粪便；废话胡说</span><br />\n\te.g.&quot;But it's still a crap shoot,&quot; he pointed out. 他指出：这仍旧是废话。<br />\n\te.g. Don't crap where you eat. I understand. 不要在你吃饭的地方拉大便，我了解。<br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">4. Damn可恶；讨厌；该死的</span><br />\n\te.g. You're stepped on my toe, damn it.该死，你踏了我的脚尖!<br />\n\te.g. She damned right and left.她乱骂一通。<br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">5. Bloody该死的；糟糕的</span><br />\n\te.g. You should have told me about it earlier. Bloody hell! 你早该告诉我的，该死的混蛋！</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/18cbc0304211c71adcf72b4057623f65.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 400px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">二、Medium 你不骂不行啊</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">1.Balls屁话；</span><br />\n\te.g. What complete and utter balls! 全是屁话！<br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">2. B**ch 婊子</span><br />\n\te.g. Son of bitch. who do you think you are? you always make me sick, little jerk! 狗崽子，您以为您是谁啊。您时常让我恶心啊，滚吧。<br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">3.Tits乳头</span><br />\n\te.g. My problem is your brain is as big as those tits. 我的毛病就是你的脑子跟胸一般大。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/30f53d692c447f5dc5eeb5a50bcf3462.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 378px; width: 400px;\" /><br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">4.Shit 狗屁；废物</span><br />\n\te.g. This is a load of shit. 这是一堆废物。<br />\n\te.g. I don't need this shit to convict you. 我不需要这些废物来指证你有罪。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/12ade5cacdaa8ef9ce5784a69aaf0a6b.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 336px; width: 400px;\" /><br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">5. Bollocks扯谈；见鬼了</span><br />\n\te.g. Oh bollocks, I've dropped my keys under the car. 唉，见鬼，我把销匙掉在车底下了。<br />\n\te.g. Now, I don't wanna be your mate, but am I talking bollocks here?现在我不想做你的朋友，但我刚才在瞎扯蛋吗？</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/676e40a90e08d3ef35c5ff26c5330971.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">三、Strong 你真欠骂啊</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">1. Bastard 杂种；王八蛋</span><br />\n\te.g. 'You bastard!' he remembered her screaming out. 你这个杂种！&rdquo; 他记得她尖叫道。<br />\n\te.g. Why does a sleazy bastard like me like whores so much?为什么像我这样的王八蛋会如此喜爱妓女？<br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">2. Dickhead白痴；笨蛋</span><br />\n\te.g. You dickhead! 你这个白痴！<br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">3.Prick变态；讨厌鬼</span><br />\n\te.g. This prick almost killed me. 这个变态差点要了我的命。<br />\n\te.g. I know this coach. he's a prick.我知道这个教练是个老滑头。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">4.Twat 笨鸟；</span><br />\n\te.g. You twat, can't you see these people have got no money? 你这个傻瓜，你看不出这些人没钱吗？</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/d8a882e0c34c383410e596bdfa3e53a5.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 249px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">四、Strongest 你妈卖批的</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">1.Cunt贱货；丑娘们</span><br />\n\te.g. My mother's house, you cunt! 去我母亲的家，你个贱货！<br />\n\te.g. Tell her the truth, you little cunt! 告诉她真相，你这个臭娘们！<br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">2.F**k</span><br />\n\t这个大家都很熟悉，就发挥想象力吧。<br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">3. Motherf**ker 臭不要脸（特指男性）</span><br />\n\te.g. This motherfucker man, won't shut up will you? 你这个臭不要脸，还不肯闭上嘴是吗？</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">(这个最强级别真的是非常不可描述的，所以大家真的慎用慎用！)<br />\n\t</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&amp;quality=80&amp;size=b9999_10000&amp;sec=1492463100965&amp;di=d71d091282516b16a490f9ab85079c73&amp;imgtype=0&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fuploads.xuexila.com%2Fallimg%2F1701%2F907-1F111141301.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t最后，英语分享几个有意思的骂人句。<br />\n\t1.Your brain has two parts. The left has nothing right, and the right has nothing left.虽然你的脑子有两个，但是左边的不靠谱，右边啥都没有。<br />\n\t2.&ldquo;Which bitch do you think you are?&quot; 你是哪门子的婊？（菲茨杰拉德）</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/bd4f0e28cd48c01c36a5528f48ffee36.jpg\" style=\"height: 399px; width: 400px;\" /><br />\n\t3. Solid gold fucking moron.大傻逼。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/04/18/1cbaba50543fb6c96095fdb6dd94cb6b.jpg\" /><br />\n\t4.Son of a biscuit.去他的小饼干。<br />\n\t5.I bet your brain feels as good as new, seeing that you&rsquo;ve never used it.我猜你大脑一定是十成新的，因为从<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">来没有见过你用脑子。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;<img src=\"https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&amp;quality=80&amp;size=b9999_10000&amp;sec=1492463610253&amp;di=fd0425994170d0e9b1bfe9ef7af1990e&amp;imgtype=0&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fd.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F5fdf8db1cb134954d29d62dd504e9258d0094a8c.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 270px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1127496/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1127496\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736148/\">有声双语美文：坚持梦想，是唯一的选择</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1157666/\">防晒霜的保质期，真的非常重要！！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1149007/\">关于all的短语和表达</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p726122/\">Quora精选：外国人眼中5个最美英文单词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1159120/\">看完《花儿与少年》，我迷上了一个人练口语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1158381/\">由于儿子不写作业，这个美国爸爸突然变网红</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px